    <p type="title" xml:lang="nob">Side forms</p>
    <p>In the <em type="italic">present </em>3pl we accept both <em type="italic">boradit </em>and <em type="italic">boradat </em>. </p>
    <p>In the <em type="italic">past </em>3sg we accept both <em type="italic">lei </em>and <em type="italic">leai </em>. </p>
    <p>In the <em type="italic">potential </em>3sg we accept both <em type="italic">leažžá </em>and <em type="italic">leaš </em>and <em type="italic">bođeža </em>and <em type="italic">bođeš </em>, and for 1pl <em type="italic">boražit </em>and <em type="italic">boražat </em>. </p>
    <p>For <em type="italic">adjective </em>comp sg the accepted forms are <em type="italic">divraseabbo </em>and <em type="italic">divrasat </em>. </p>
